{"tid":1002554,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"親生兒僅值56萬！夫妻離婚把人帶走　祖父苦尋一年才知「孫已被賣掉」","createTime":"2019-01-31T04:40:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-31T06:22:51.000Z","uid":212399,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"576cb94198815c07f352db6f64405b05e254d458","tid":1002554,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T04:40:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3875/3875216.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3875%2F3875216.jpg&h=76ab4ffe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲馮老先生找了一年才找到孫子。（圖／翻攝自泉州晚報）<br />\n國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n大陸福建晉江一對夫妻先前因為鬧分手，竟將親生的3歲兒子浩浩（化名），以12萬人民幣的價格（約56萬台幣）的價格，賣給一對沒有生育的夫婦。事後，浩浩的祖父母感到奇怪，原本跟他們住一起的孫子被帶走後，就再也沒有回來過，追問之下才得知小孩已經被賣掉的消息，趕緊到警局報案，終於在尋人近一年後將浩浩找回。<br />\n根據陸媒報導，浩浩自從出生之後，一直以來都是由住在福建晉江的馮姓祖父母扶養，而他的親生父母則是偶而會來探望他。2018年1月，浩浩被父母接走後超過3天沒有回家，而他的祖父母卻再也連絡不上這對夫妻，只能到處打聽消息，想找回孫子。<br />\n過沒多久，馮老先生得知兒子因為販毒坐牢，申請探監之後才得知，孫子浩浩早就被賣掉，於是趕緊到警局報案。據悉，浩浩的父母因為要分手，於是協議將親生小孩賣給一對住在安海、多年未生育的蘇氏夫婦，得手的56萬台幣則由兩人平花用。<br />\n大陸警方在本月16日晚間，到蘇氏夫婦家中將人拘捕，並成功地將浩浩帶出。報導中指出，馮老先生的兒子因涉嫌犯下拐賣婦女兒童罪嫌，將被追究刑事責任，而購買小孩的蘇氏夫婦也犯有同樣的罪嫌，必須接受法律制裁，目前整起事件也還在調查當中。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190131/1370094.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190131%2F1370094.htm&d=h41GIreLF%2BIJLuW8J2uc6oLj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=c16ac1c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190131/1370094.htm</a>"},{"pid":"d6bef2a283eb66fc068dac05b31a652341d0f448","tid":1002554,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T04:42:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ec6ea58ee257ac4af4c3ce3768576d47f58137a","tid":1002554,"uid":207349,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T04:43:15.000Z","msg":"又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8e72a0ecdbb471fd0342b588a973fbd900be1db","tid":1002554,"uid":157197,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T05:30:52.000Z","msg":"可能夾埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n賣仔拎錢 阿爺阿嫲報公安搵孫<br />\n<br />\n拉買家又拎得返個孫<br />\n<br />\n錢同人雙收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0134f05e06b855e3cb039fb5307414c1e6716d3","tid":1002554,"uid":61832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8e72a0ecdbb471fd0342b588a973fbd900be1db","tid":1002554,"uid":157197,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T05:30:52.000Z","msg":"可能夾埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n賣仔拎錢 阿爺阿嫲報公安搵孫<br />\n<br />\n拉買家又拎得返個孫<br />\n<br />\n錢同人雙收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T05:36:02.000Z","msg":"無限賣"},{"pid":"b6b129dc324eebef19535e8907cec78321340601","tid":1002554,"uid":166792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8e72a0ecdbb471fd0342b588a973fbd900be1db","tid":1002554,"uid":157197,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T05:30:52.000Z","msg":"可能夾埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n賣仔拎錢 阿爺阿嫲報公安搵孫<br />\n<br />\n拉買家又拎得返個孫<br />\n<br />\n錢同人雙收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T05:37:51.000Z","msg":"再賣過"},{"pid":"2a9a7a40c65b68ba9b3d4e07118afbfaf250677a","tid":1002554,"uid":55585,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T05:50:21.000Z","msg":"陶瓷娃娃"},{"pid":"c4cd2257c77acf97583cd98c4915745eee4bd8a4","tid":1002554,"uid":19712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T05:51:47.000Z","msg":"會唔會個孫都係偷返黎 就算拎唔返都無所謂"},{"pid":"e0c33dab46cb8b5a5aeaa62f6ff9046c09e0cfdc","tid":1002554,"uid":199907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"576cb94198815c